title: GWT compile errors
body:
#### Issue details
Gdx core failed to compile with GWT

#### Reproduction steps/code
[Follow wiki steps in order to run libgdx tests](https://github.com/libgdx/libgdx/wiki/Running-Tests) then run `bash ../../gradlew superDev` from **tests/gdx-tests-gwt** project.

#### Version of LibGDX and/or relevant dependencies
master branch since commit 3eede16860c339c639ae02552ec348f1432e9afe
I tried just before this commit and all go well, so my assumption is this issue is related to recent @Tom-Ski changes.

Sorry, I'm not familiar with GWT to provide a fix myself.
